BACKEND:-
1. npm i ts-node typescript nodemon @types/express @types/cors @types/node --save-dev
2. npx tsc --init

FRONTEND:-
1. npm create vite@latest
2. npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
3. npx tailwindcss init -p
4. paste this in tsconfig.json
"baseUrl": ".",
    "paths": {
      "@/*": [
        "./src/*"
      ]
}
follow this documentation link:- https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/installation/vite
5. we are using lucide-react for icons

6. auth0:- go to auth0.com and create an application there
:- npm i @auth0/auth0-react (in frontend folder)


